==English==
===Phrase===
'''[[let]] [[alone]]'''
#{{idiom}} Or even; [[much less]]; to say nothing of.  
#:''I didn't even notice it, '''let alone''' care.''

===Verb===
'''let alone'''
#''(transitive)'' To [[leave]] alone; to stop bothering.
#:''I wish he would '''let me alone''' so I could get some sleep.''